CyberSource version 0.01
========================

CyberSource is one of the leading E-Commerce service providers.
This library implements a generic routine to send requests
to the CyberSource and obtain results using ICS2 API library.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

ICS2 is a proprietary API to CyberSource E-Commerce services.
It should be properly obtained from www.cybersource.com
when creating CyberSource merchan account.

